cu.explanation_en: Changing the GNB IPv4 address for NG AMF to an IP in the AMF's subnet (192.168.70.x) causes potential IP conflict and routing issues, preventing proper communication with the AMF.

du.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
du.explanation_en: Setting the remote N address to an unreachable IP (10.0.0.1) instead of the loopback address prevents the DU from establishing connection with the CU, leading to F1 interface failure.
